('spirited-away-2001', 'Spirited Away', 'movie', 129, 'tt0245429', 34, 8.6, 970141, 2001, 'Unknown', 'Movie', '2j 04m', 'IMDb 8.6', 'Seorang anak perempuan berusia 10 tahun semakin jauh dari orangtuanya, memasuki dunia yang dikuasai oleh para binatang aneh yang mirip monster. Akankah dia bisa melihat kembali dunia seperti semula?', '/39wmItIWsg5sZMyRUHLkWBcuVCM.jpg', '/dyJvKsNs2KP8qQnAXbRwDjblViy.jpg', array['Adventure', 'Animation', 'Family'], false, false, true),
('city-of-god-2002', 'City of God', 'movie', 598, 'tt0317248', 35, 8.6, 872542, 2002, 'Unknown', 'Movie', '2j 10m', 'IMDb 8.6', 'In the poverty-stricken favelas of Rio de Janeiro in the 1970s, two young men choose different paths. Rocket is a budding photographer who documents the increasing drug-related violence of his neighborhood, while José “Zé” Pequeno is an ambitious drug dealer diving into a dangerous life of crime.', '/k7eYdWvhYQyRQoU2TB2A2Xu2TfD.jpg', '/uvitbjFU4JqvMwIkMWHp69bmUzG.jpg', array['Crime', 'Drama'], false, false, true),
